{"tid":857173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔愛自己國家嘅人 乜撚嘢都唔會愛","createTime":"2018-10-11T03:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T14:20:50.000Z","uid":18245,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e884cfe81bb75cdcb1946b67d4774bd16b1c82a","tid":857173,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">No army can stop an idea whose time has come</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDGz0yD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDGz0yD.jpg&h=667a39c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每日150個殖民<br />\n消滅我地嘅語言<br />\n搶曬我地嘅資源<br />\n\b<br />\n咁多年黎班所謂嘅政客<br />\n為我地爭取左乜野？<br />\n鉛水？ 奶粉荒？大白象？去第三世界發展嘅機會？<br />\n唔好話無床位生仔<br />\n我地係連住嘅地方都比佢地搶撚埋啊！<br />\n你仲咁夠疆要我地科水<br />\n我屌你老母啊！！<br />\n<br />\n我地屋企比人任食任攞 周圍痾屎<br />\n仲要我地幫佢地抆屎<br />\n但唔少人諗緊嘅竟然係將自己屋企拱手相讓<br />\n自己就搞盡腦汁去第二度生活<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">走佬？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地真係走得甩咩？</span></span></span><br />\n班蝗蟲佈滿全球 你走得去邊？？<br />\n<br />\n你班蝗蟲咁鐘意講錢 我地就講下錢 20年黎<br />\n三跑 支鐵 港珠澳大橋 西九.etc<br />\n有邊次唔係香港人埋單？<br />\n今次講緊成萬億港紙比你去吊住條命<br />\n你仲好意思講 無支那香港早就收左皮？<br />\n無香港 你支那早就收鳩左皮啦<br />\n<br />\n我地忍撚夠啦！<br />\n一路以黎 好多義士不惜犧牲自己<br />\n黎為香港嘅未來鋪路 今次到我地啦<br />\n輪到我地守護我地嘅家圍<br />\n<br />\n我唔想我地留比下一代嘅野<br />\n就只係聽唔明我地講嘅野<br />\n我亦希望我地嘅下一代唔再係<br />\n香港市民而係香港國民"},{"pid":"81fd815cd0ad53ac72bfcd329e35879132c9b06d","tid":857173,"uid":18245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:02:18.000Z","msg":"再唔企出黎就唔會再有機會企出黎架啦！！"},{"pid":"b5ce3f3f92ef18ab0170f1f14a732855ac12b743","tid":857173,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:16:25.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11ed84f1ebb3acb2511a5a64a17672e36372e42","tid":857173,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:16:42.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e47ffa44ee5d2d2091c28ea07620644445ac17","tid":857173,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:16:54.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df1b3416fd6ae1125678e7b49761e064332c7f8","tid":857173,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:17:04.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d50c23f52a236a7623cdd23e63500e2b2ade69","tid":857173,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:17:14.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7f0f7a2446b15bb7a6795176dfa81aab5189fc","tid":857173,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:17:24.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f91ae13399ed26752dab963ba190cec0f159fa","tid":857173,"uid":204229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325af52902329c53aec26403f35b1f0b6f139e47","tid":857173,"uid":206673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f506e3791ba5878c9b0c525edcb636a46d5e889","tid":857173,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:20:50.000Z","msg":"打倒共產黨！大家盡量每日向身邊朋友宣揚反共意識，光復指日可待"}]}